data.description: Motivated Seller!!! This stunning 5-bedroom, 2-bathroom house is now available for sale! This charming property boasts an impressive size of 2,752 square feet, providing ample space for you and your loved ones to create lasting memories.    Step inside and be greeted by the warm ambiance that fills every room. The living spaces are thoughtfully designed to provide both comfort and functionality. With a newly installed roof in 2023, this home offers peace of mind and protection from the elements for years to come.    Imagine spending lazy summer days lounging by the inviting inground pool. Whether you seek relaxation or a place to entertain family and friends, this private oasis is perfect for both. Take a refreshing dip or simply bask in the sun's rays – the choice is yours!    Cooking enthusiasts will delight in the remodeled kitchen, which features modern appliances and ample counter space. Prepare delicious meals while enjoying the company of loved ones in the adjacent dining area.    The five well-appointed bedrooms offer plenty of space for rest and relaxation. Each room is a haven with an abundance of natural light filtering through, creating a soothing ambiance.    This property offers convenience at your doorstep. Explore nearby parks, schools, shopping centers, and restaurants – all just moments away.    Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your dream home. Schedule a showing today and discover why 5 Johnson Avenue is the perfect place to build a future filled with joy and happiness.
